description			"IG-88

Class: Wookiee.
Class Summary: 
A dual wielding tank class with powerful sniper and strong melee attacks. 

Weaponry:
- Pulse Cannon *
- Droid Melee *
- Dual Blaster Rifles (Based on Westar level 3)
- Thermal Detonator/Self Destruct
- Melee (Fists)

* Special Weapon Descriptions:
--- Pulse Cannon
- Based on Projectile Rifle
- Ignites enemies on successful hits

--- Droid Melee *
- Based on lightsaber
- Can use Red and Dual styles
- Cannot block blaster or lightsaber attacks
- Bounces off walls on swings
- Knocks down enemies within a small radius on wall hits

Attributes:
- Magnetic Plating
- Cortosis Armor
- Blast Armor
- Shield Regeneration (1)
- Strength (2)
- Radar (Perma-sense 1)

Abilities:
- Fast hacking

Each droid of the IG-88 series shared the same consciousness. These assassin droids were collectively one of the galaxy's most infamous bounty hunters."